Class ErdosRenyiGraphGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • GraphCreation.GraphLoader
      • GraphCreation.ErdosRenyiGraphGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeneratedGraph

    public class ErdosRenyiGraphGenerator
extends GraphLoader
implements GeneratedGraph
    Graph Generator that creates a random graph using the Erdos-Renyi binomial model (each pair of vertices is connected with probability p) This does not support DIRECTED graphs and wraps the JUNG ErdosRenyiGenerator Functionality
    Author:
    MOREPOWER
